description:
A simple dish that anyone can enjoy! Inspired by my all time favorite sonic ship, Bardonic (Sonic the Hedgehog x Bartleby) Makes for a great dinner and desert in one. I usually eat this while eating sonic underground because it makes me feel good but you can eat it while watching whatever you want like my bardonic amv's.

What you will need:
1 Ramen packet(Beef or chicken packet is optional
1 1/2 cans of Blue raspberry soda
1 banana, yellow like Bartleby's hair.
